[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

With 15 points and a 5-card Major you open 1\S. Partner responds 3\S.  

Your 15 points gets revalued to 16/17 for the singleton. Add partner's 10-12 and you have enough for game. So you bid 4\S.}

