[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

With 13 points you open 1\S. Partner responds 3\S.  

Figure partner for 11-12 points. You have 13 but could revalue to 14 with the doubleton \H. But the truth is that your points are not very good ones. You should pass.}

